## 2 · Color System (Design Tokens v2)

> **Principles**
> *One heroic hue (blue) + one success hue (teal)*. Everything else is neutral so hashes, charts, and data stand out.
>
> | House Spirit           | Borrowed Principle                       | Runix Hub Manifestation                                            |
> | ---------------------- | ---------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |
> | **Apple**              | *Relentless simplicity + tactile delight* | Ultra-clean layouts, intuitive touch targets, subtle depth, and delightful micro-interactions. |
> | **OpenAI**             | *Clarity over flair; API-first*           | One accent color, minimal chrome, every UI action maps to a documented endpoint. |
> | **GitHub**             | *Social coding rituals + version control* | Fork → verify → merge workflows for scientific protocols.         |
> | **Linear**             | *Minimalist focus + motion polish*        | Clean cards, smooth hover states, purposeful animations.          |
> | **Vercel**             | *Performance obsession + developer UX*    | Sub-second loads; every action feels instant.                     |
> | **Observable**         | *Notebook-driven exploration*             | Interactive data views; every chart links to underlying code.     |
> | **Papers With Code**   | *Reproducibility as first principle*      | Verification badges; hash ribbons; reproducibility scores.

