## 6 · Motion Grammar

| Purpose               | Duration    | Curve                                 | Example                          |
| --------------------- | ----------- | ------------------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| **Navigate**          | 250 ms      | `cubic-bezier(.22,.61,.36,1)`         | Switching tabs                   |
| **Confirm Success**   | 400 ms      | spring (Framer Motion, stiffness 150) | Verification pulse               |
| **Draw Attention**    | 800 ms loop | linear                                | Live pipeline spinner            |
| **Negative Feedback** | 80 ms × 3   | `ease-out`                            | Shake for failed reproducibility |

Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`: replace animations with opacity fades.

